#HELPS

-1 BUILDING BUILD BUILDINGS 'BUILDING A HOUSE' PROPERTY~
/---------------------------------------------------------------------\
|          Building a House                                           |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Players now have the ability to purchase and own houses. This option is
only available to players with accounts who have been noted
as active roleplayers. 

To purchase your house, you will need to do the following:

-Find an architect to build your house in a city, and pay the requisite fee.
Note: The average house will cost 1,000,000 copper per room.

-You will be contacted by the immortals once you have paid the required fee.
 At this point, you will be contacted about providing a location, description,
and any additional amenities you would like to purchase for your house.


Your house will appear as an entrance available in the room where it is constructed.

For example, if your house is a wooden cabin, you might see:

A stout wooden cabin is here.

You can enter your house via the ENTER command. 

Ex: Enter Cabin

If you have a problem or question about your house, please address it in a note to IMMORTAL.

~

