-1 'ACCOUNT RULES' 'RULES OF ACCOUNTING' 'ACCOUNT RULE'~
/---------------------------------------------------------------------\
|               Account Rules                                         |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

The following are mandatory rules for anyone using accounts:

I. Only one account per person is allowed. Attempting to
create multiple accounts is considered a violation of the
rules.

II. Do not give your account password to any other player, or
attempt to acquire the password of another player.

III. Your account is an out of character relationship between your
various characters. It is not an excuse for multi-charring!


