Some psionic focuses exert a temporary affect (such as shove), while
others exert a lasting influence (such as Paranoia). Lasting psionic
effects drain mana from the psionicist for as long as they are in
effect. Unlike magical affects, psionic influences last until their
victim can overcome the will of the psionicist, rather than having
a fixed duration.

Psionicists can maintain a maximum of eight focuses at once. Some
focuses will require more than one focus slot to maintain, and
the total number of foci possible will increase over the course
of the psionicists career.

To get a list of their current focuses, FOCUS by itself will 
provide the psionicist with a list. 

To end a focus, a psionicist can UNFOCUS the slot number (given in
the focus list). 

