|      Offhand Disarm                                                 |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Syntax: Offhand

Requiring more precision that the standard disarm skill, the offhand
disarm is practiced by the swordmasters, who can use it to remove 
items carried in an opponent's offhand.

