/---------------------------------------------------------------------\ 
|         Rebirth                                                     |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Syntax: Cast 'Rebirth' <Target>

The rebirth spell is a powerful healing spell of the sphere of water.
Rebirth will completely heal a person's wounds, but it will weaken
their strength of body and health temporarily, due to the comprehensive
nature of the healing. Rebirth can not be cast in rapid succession on
a person.

~





