\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Syntax: Emote <message>

The emote command works by emoting an action that you
do to the rest of the room. 

Example:
If your name is Jolinn, and you type:

Emote rambles on and on about killing arch-devils.

Everyone else in the room would see:
