/---------------------------------------------------------------------\ 
|         Agony                                                       |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Syntax: Cast 'Agony' <target>

Under the influence of the sphere of void, this spell can be used
to inflict enormous amounts of pain on another. Creatures or 
persons affected by agony will find that any attempt to perform
a skill or action can be impeded by the affects of the pain, 
resulting in a diminished skill level. Agony also saps the
strength of the affected person, the pain inducing a weakness
in muscular response.

~

-1  POX~
