The pox spell attempts to infect the victim with one of the 
wasting illnesses that often infest creatures of places of
great negative energy, such as the Void. Along with a loss 
of strength, it also reduces the ability to act, as they are 
devoured internally by the horrible affliction. Highly 
contagius, more virulent poxes have been known to wipe out
entire villages.
~


