scholars of void is the spell of the deathwalk, which inflicts 
not only the caster's immediate surroundings, but an entire
area around him. For the duration of the deathwalk curse, no
corpses may be sacrificed. Most horrifyingly, the corpses of
all creatures slain arise from the slumber of death, animating
