-1 'FIND FAMILIAR'~
/---------------------------------------------------------------------\ 
|         Find Familiar                                               |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

One of the most time consuming spells an initate of the void can
cast is the spell of find familiar. Delving through the prime
material, the magi seeks a familiar which resonates with his
or her own dark soul. The familiar a scholar takes is determined
at birth, and does not change throughout the scholar's life.
The coming of a familiar brings more health and a greater ability
to channel magic for the caster, but carries with it a price: Should
a familiar die, the caster will bear the pain of its loss until their
own death. Familiars also have special abilities, that the caster
will have to discover on their own.

