\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Damage done varies depending on many factors, including the
quality of your weapon, additional modifiers to your ability
to do damage from equipment or spells, and skills such as enhanced
or brutal damage.

In order from the least damage to the most, the damages are as follows:

miss          maul          DISMEMBER      ANNHILATE
scratch       decimate      MASSACRE       ERADICATE
graze         devastate     MANGLE         
hit           maim          DEMOLISH
injure        MUTILATE      DEVASTATE
wound         DISEMBOWEL    OBLITERATE

At the far reaches of damage, UNSPEAKABLE things have been known
to occur.

