-1 REWARD~
/---------------------------------------------------------------------\
|       REWARD                                                        |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

       Those in violation of the laws set forth by the Guardians of Law 
are marked as targets of Iandir's wrath by the appearance of (REWARD) 
upon their person. Any citizen of Avendar who takes the life of such a 
criminal is bestowed a divine gift from Iandir.
       For those who have not reached the rank of hero, the reward takes 
the form of battle experience, aiding them in attaining their next rank. 
For those who have reached the rank of hero, the reward takes the form 
of partial practice sessions.

