Detect theft, Set Trap, Contact Agent, Investigate Death

~

-1 ASSASSIN ASSASSINS~
/---------------------------------------------------------------------\
|       ASSASSIN                                                      |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Profession: Rogue.
Class:      Assassin.

   Masters of death, assassins have perfected the art of stealth
the pursuit of their craft.  They strike from the shadows, using
knife, poison, and dart as their tools.  Assassins each have their own
meaning for their actions - some devoted to the extermination of evil,
others nothing more than the fattening of their own purse, but they all
find unity in their perfection of the dealing of death.  
 
 
Assassin skills include:
 
taint, cloak, dart, exploit

~

