|       SWORDMASTER                                                   |
\---------------------------------------------------------------------/

Profession: Warrior.
Class:      Swordmaster.

  Swordmasters are warriors who have devoted their life to mastering
one weapon - the blade.  Learned in ancient meditative techniques,
they practice the art of ak'anginta: thought-to-form, where the
blade becomes an extension of self, and acquires form.  Using these "Ginta"
